snippet.title: Super Mario Eclipse | Initial F3 2020 Trailer [OUTDATED]
snippet.description: Our big project is finally unveiled! It's come a long way from a simple mod to change the lighting in Delfino Plaza. Now, it's an ambitious project to completely revamp Super Mario Sunshine and increase content threefold! I hope everyone likes our project, and we'll hopefully have a definitive release date soon! Thanks again to all of the wonderful people collaborating on this project with us; this is truly the Sunshine community's greatest achievement!
